</style>

<!-- SERVICE CARDS -->
<section style="padding:0 24px 80px;background:#EAF5FB;">
  <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="svc-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:20px;">
      <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:12px;padding:30px 26px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Egress Window Installation</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0 0 18px;flex:1;">We cut in new egress windows for basement bedrooms, additions, and finishing projects, sized to Lincoln's current code. Every install includes the window well, drainage, and a final walkthrough so you know exactly what you're getting.</p>
        <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#2FA34D;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Learn More &#8594;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/egress-window-replacement-lincoln/" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:12px;padding:30px 26px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Egress Window Replacement</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0 0 18px;flex:1;">Old, undersized, or rotted-out egress windows get swapped for a new frame and glass without tearing up your whole foundation wall. Most replacements are done in a day, and we haul away the old unit.</p>
        <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#2FA34D;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Learn More &#8594;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/window-well-installation-lincoln/" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:12px;padding:30px 26px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Window Well Installation & Drainage</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0 0 18px;flex:1;">A window well that doesn't drain will eventually flood your basement, so we grade, gravel, and pipe every well we set to move water away from the house. We also fit new wells to existing egress windows that were installed without one.</p>
        <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#2FA34D;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Learn More &#8594;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/basement-window-replacement-lincoln/" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:12px;padding:30px 26px;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.06);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Basement Window Replacement</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0 0 18px;flex:1;">Not every basement window needs to become an egress window, and we'll tell you straight if a simple like-for-like replacement is the better call. We handle standard basement window swaps with the same one-day crew and cleanup.</p>
        <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#2FA34D;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Learn More &#8594;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 1000px) { .svc-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr) !important; } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .svc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; } }
</style>

<!-- WHY -->
<section style="padding:84px 24px;background:#fff;">
  <div class="why-grid" style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;gap:64px;align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">What Makes Us Different</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(26px,3.4vw,40px);margin:0 0 28px;">Licensed, Insured, and Built for Nebraska Winters</h2>
      <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
          <li style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2FA34D" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 4px;">Most Cut-Ins Finished in One Day</p>
              <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5A6B76;margin:0;">We show up with the crew and equipment to cut, frame, and set your egress window and well in a single visit, weather permitting.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2FA34D" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 4px;">Code-Compliant Sizing, Every Time</p>
              <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5A6B76;margin:0;">We size and place every egress window to current IRC and Lincoln-Lancaster County requirements so your basement bedroom actually counts as legal.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2FA34D" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 4px;">Free Written Estimates</p>
              <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5A6B76;margin:0;">You get a firm number in writing before we touch your foundation, no verbal quotes that change once the digging starts.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2FA34D" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 4px;">24/7 Line for Deadlines and Emergencies</p>
              <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#5A6B76;margin:0;">Closing on a house, dealing with a flooded well, or facing an inspection deadline? Call anytime and we'll work you into the schedule.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
      <div style="border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 18px 44px rgba(10,61,92,0.2);aspect-ratio:4/5;">
        <img src="/images/hero-800.webp" alt="Lincoln Egress Windows at work" width="800" height="800" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;">
        <div style="background:#1273A8;border-radius:14px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin:0;line-height:1;">$0</p>
          <p style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);margin:6px 0 0;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">Estimate Fee</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#2FA34D;border-radius:14px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
          <p style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin:0;line-height:1;">Same Day</p>
          <p style="font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);margin:6px 0 0;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;">Most Repairs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
